      "rationale": "The analysis was executed by a senior FEA engineer (8 years orthopedic implant FEA experience) following a pre-approved analysis plan (DS-AP-2023-0047, rev. B). Boundary conditions (fixed base plate, applied displacement at superior fixture), material property assignments (Ti-6Al-4V ELI per ASTM F136), and contact pair definitions were independently reviewed by a second senior engineer prior to any results extraction. Review sign-off is recorded in the PLM system. Gradation 2 achieved."
