      "rationale": "Material properties (E, σ_y, E_t) were sourced from lot-specific tensile test certificates for the Ti-6Al-4V ELI bar stock used to manufacture the test constructs (DS-MAT-2023-0089). Screw geometry was digitized via CMM (Zeiss Contura G2) with measurement uncertainty < 0.01 mm. Friction coefficient (μ = 0.2 ± 0.05) was determined from dedicated pin-on-disk tribology tests at the test conditions (DS-TRIB-2022-0003). Sensitivity analysis identified E and σ_y as the dominant input parameters (Sobol indices 0.38 and 0.29 respectively). Combined input uncertainty contribution: 1.2% of stiffness QoI, 1.8% of yield force QoI. Both within the 2% acceptance threshold. Gradation 3 achieved."
